Hey friends! I ordered spicy chicken steamed momos and veg steamed momos. The veg momos were not so appealing in taste..it was average. However, the chicken momos were good. Worth price. The sauce needs improvement again..üòÖ
The experience was not completely bad. Worth money that's all I can say.

Ordered Chicken Spicy Momos and Chicken n Onion Momos through Swiggy. Packaging was perfect.
Comming to the taste, the Onion n Chicken momos tasted a little bland and the Spicy Chicken Momos were more of a spicy version of onion chicken momos. Overall they were just ok, not a fan of these though.

Ordered Chicken Popcorn and Veg. Machurian roll. Packing is good. But, instead of Veg manchurian we got Cheese roll and the taste is very disappointing. Coming to chicken popcorn it smelled like it had done 3 days back. The food is horrible.
PS: My suggestion is don't order the food from Snack Point. If you visit the place and have food there and itself it will be a best option.

Ordered chicken momo and chicken burger from here. Chicken momos are filled with onions and are very small. Burger was tasty. The patty was good.
Quick bites were good in taste. French fries, momos, veg kebabs and potato wedges were crunchy and tasty. Good for spending time with open food court-self service.
